# Slash Commands System
> Authority: See authority.mdc

**Session-based project management with evidence trails across multiple work sessions.**

## Commands
- **`/analyze project [context]`** (`/a`) - Analysis & research sessions 【PLAN】
- **`/design project [context]`** (`/d`) - Design & planning sessions 【PLAN】  
- **`/implement project [context]`** (`/i`) - Implementation & testing sessions 【PLAN】
- **`/close`** (`/c`) - Session closure & documentation finalization 【VALIDATE】

## Workflow
1. Command loads project history from `agent_work/project/`
2. Creates session doc from `templates/` 【PLAN】
3. Guided work with evidence collection 【VALIDATE】 
4. `/close` finalizes docs + creates next-session handoffs 【STOP】

## Templates
- `/analyze` uses `templates/analysis-session-template.md`
- `/design` uses `templates/design-session-template.md`
- `/implement` uses `templates/implementation-session-template.md`
- Master tracking uses `templates/progress-tracking-template.md`